column5: Any construction on Hwy 105 this year between Hwy 17 and Red Lake?

Nope. The bridges they were working on last year all seem to be done and the road is smooth. Edit - at least as far as Pakwash - I didn't go the last 20 miles to Red Lake. But the bridge over the Chukuni looked done, at least from going underneath it
Appreciate the info on Hwy 105. Looking forward to a smooth trip. Heading up in 4 weeks and getting antsy.
